### Dino-World runtime ###
# Secrets — never commit. Copy .env.example → .env locally.
.env
# SQLite database + WAL/SHM sidecar files (runtime dir at project root).
# Anchored to root with the leading slash so we don't accidentally match
# `src/main/resources/data/` where game catalog assets live.
/data/
# Compressed nightly backups produced by scripts/backup.sh.
/backups/
# Rolling log files produced by Logback.
/logs/